<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px; }
        .container { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; }
        .code { background-color: #eee; padding: 10px; font-family: monospace; }
        .warning { color: #990000; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to the Net, {{ character.characterName }}!</h1>
        <p>Your Code & Conquest profile is now active. You can now use your unique Access Key to interact with the game API.</p>
        <p class="warning"><strong>Important:</strong> This is the only time you will see your key. Store it somewhere safe and do not share it.</p>
        <p>Your Access Key is:</p>
        <div class="code">{{ character.apiKey }}</div>
        <hr>
        <p>Good luck, Netrunner.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>